sentences.english: The Browns are all college graduates.

sentences.english: He was the first one graduated in China medical school and became a practitioner i…

sentences.english: This year's graduates with major in Automation Control or Electrical Engineering are also welcome.

sentences.english: This is among the best-paid professions for people with just a college degree.

sentences.english: "eople are saying this is the worst year to graduate, ever, " she said in a telephone interview.

sentences.english: A new wave of graduates are scrambling for lots in some companies and factories.
sentences.chinese: 一羣剛出校門的畢業生正在公司或工廠中爭取空缺。
